data.description:
The perfect corner lot awaits, with an amazing view of the mountains & has an excellent location! Conveniently located near dining, shopping, parks, schools, & more. This fully-fenced property offers a lovely desert front yard w/palm trees & a detached 2-car garage. Captivating open floor plan boasts vaulted beamed ceilings, beautiful wood-look flooring, fresh paint, Arcadia doors, & a welcoming living room w/stone-wall fireplace & a picture-perfect window. The generously sized family room has patio access. Impressive kitchen includes sophisticated light fixtures, a gas cooktop, a wall oven, a wine fridge, quartz counters, a farmhouse sink, a breakfast bar, & a breakfast nook. Oversized main suite has a sitting area w/French doors to the backyard, & a pristine ensuite for added comfort. Another primary retreat provides outdoor access, a walk-in closet, & a private aesthetic bathroom w/dual sinks. Relax on the full-length covered patio w/ceiling fans in the well-sized backyard w/a fire pit & a separate workshop area. Don't let this one get away!

A small portion of the lot is in potential sale pending bank approval, survey is in the document tab for your convenience.
